Enum GameConfiguration.CharState

    GameConfiguration

    public static enum GameConfiguration.CharState
extends java.lang.Enum<GameConfiguration.CharState>
    The state of the CharacterLabel

    CONTAIN_AND_RIGHT_POSITION means that the answer includes the char and the char is at right position.

    CONTAIN_BUT_WRONG_POSITION means that the answer includes the char but the char is at wrong position.

    DO_NOT_CONTAIN means that the answer doesn't includes the char.

    EMPTY means that the label is empty.
